      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "I can see that GitHub's file changes view shows only one file at a time due to the large number of changes. This is because the reference implementation includes dependencies and auxiliary materials:\r\n\r\n- The reference code uses [secp256k1lab](https://github.com/secp256k1lab/secp256k1lab) python library (vendored as a git subtree, ~20 files) for scalar and group arithmetic. I can remove this from the PR when this library is integrated in this repository (#1855).\r\n- Auxiliary files include `docs/partialsig_forgery.md` (which I can move to a gist if preferred) and a test vector generation script (~1400 lines). I can exclude these if necessary.",
